    <note>Zhou(1) Wo [507] Zhejiang TZ, 123.31a. This is the first Suichang jinshi of this surname and only the second Song Suichang jinshi after Gong(2) Yuan [941] (qv.) He has the same generational name as Zhou(1) Chi 476], father of Mou [11561] and son-in-law of Liu(2) Yi [1201] (qv.). Wo is probably also the son-in-law of Zeng(1) Gongliang [8136] (or at least a cousin of his son-in-law) whose mingzi, Tai, is identical except for one stroke. XCB, 271.15a, 277.14a, 284.1a.</note>
